To run the code: Use the mininet vm, On it using the command 'sudo python topology.py' run the the custom topology.
The program will ask for no. of hosts per switch and no. of switches as input. Enter integers.

Even hosts can only talk to even hosts and odd hosts can only talk to odd numbered hosts.
Odd numbered hosts have bw of 1Mb and even numbered hosts have a bw of 2Mb.
